inn1.comm: banged in short outside off stump and that's been left alone to the keeper
short of a length outside off, leaves that one through to the keeper
short of a good length outside off, this one holds its line and it's been left alone to the keeper
shortish on leg stump, straying in line slightly, turned down towards fine leg for a single
short of a good length on the off, tried to crunch it through extra cover, mistimes it towards mid-on
shortish on the off, rocks back and defends him solidly towards extra cover
accurate start, on the off stump, lands on a good length, Wade gets forward and defends it back to the bowler
goodish length on middle, Wade gets front and across and drives it back to the bowler
short of a good length on middle, rocks on the back foot and pats it back down the pitch
pitched up and it's been driven beautifully through the covers in the deep, nicely timed, the fielder at extra cover got a hand to it
goodish length on the off, gets on the back foot and defends it towards point
short of a good length on the off, Wade plays it form the crease, gets an inside edge into the ribs
short of a length outside off, chops it down on the bounce towards point
pitched up on the off stump, driven through towards mid-on, can't beat that fielder
short of a good length and he watches that one through to the keeper
ooh, just wide of the diving square leg fielder, full toss on middle and it's flicked away firmly, a full length dive to the right but it's in vain
short of a length outside off, chops that one towards point from the crease
short of a good length on the off, punches it into the off side from the crease
lands on a length on middle, seems quite nippy, on target, pushes that one back to the bowler
a thick outside edge, full and wide and he goes hard at that one, gets a thick edge past slip down to the third-man boundary
shortish on leg stump, turned away towards fine leg for a single
short of a good length, comes down the track to flay it through point, goes hard at it and misses
shortish on middle, drops it down in front of square leg and steals a quick single
lands on a length on the off, that's been driven towards mid-off on the front foot, didn't time it well
shortish outside off, crunches it off the back foot towards point
times this one better, pitched up on middle, it's driven down the pitch, mid-off cuts it off, they just get a single
superbly struck, short of a good length, gets on the back foot and crunches it through the covers for a boundary, took a while to get to the boundary though, a slow outfield this
kept a little low, shortish, goes for the cut, misses, it zips through under his bat
shortish on middle, punched off the back foot in front of mid-on
short and it comes on to him a little quicker than he expected, shortish, went for the pull, tried to smash it through midwicket, got an inside edge onto the thigh
shortish on the off, punched through point and cover for a couple of runs, a bit of a fumble as the fielder slides and tries to throw back
plenty of width there for him to free his arms, short and it's been slashed hard through point for a boundary
short of a good length on the off, pushed to the right of cover for a quick single
shortish on leg stump, tries to turn that one fine, gets it behind square for a single
shortish again down the leg side, whipped through to fine leg for a single
short outside off, cut that one down towards third man for a single
goes hard at that one, pitched it fuller, tried to drive it through extra cover, got a thick outside edge, actually ended up slicing that towards third man
length ball and he cashes in, slams it over mid-on for a one bounce four, nicely hit, two bounces in fact
thrashed, short and wide and that's been hit hard past point, good fielding by the man at third man, runs to his left and dives to haul it back in, that's 1,000 runs for Warner in ODI cricket
that's out, there was a noise, short of a length, tried to chop it through point, a faint nick through the keeper, big cheers all round, there's a trumpet blowing somewhere, Shapoor Zadran's ecstatic
goodish length on middle, gets across and pushes it back to the bowler
pitched on a length outside off, opens the face a little to drive it towards third man for a single
short of a good length outside off, pushed towards point from the crease
nicely timed, angling in and it's driven past mid-on, the fielder dives over the ball, just a couple in the end
shortish on middle, rocks back and knocks it down into the leg side
pitched on a length and it's been driven back firmly to the bowler
pitched up outside off, that's been dug out towards point from the crease, almost yorker length
drops that one short outside off, runs that towards third man, the fielder takes a while to get to it and he scrambles back for the second
shortish on the off, gets on the back foot and punches it to extra cover
short of a good length on the off, drops that one down towards the short point fielder
pitched up on middle, that's driven down towards mid-on from the crease
short of a good length on middle, rocks back and defends it towards mid-on
width is what Wade wanted and he got it, short of a good length and it's blazed through point and cover for a boundary
short of a good length, gets on the back foot and defends it towards mid-on
nips back in, maybe he cut it back in, struck in the ribs as he tried to play it off the back foot
short of a good length, punched towards cover from the crease
bowled that full on the off and that's been driven straight to mid-off
shortish outside off, cut away towards third man for a single
beaten, Wade played a little inside the line to that one, could have actually nipped away a hint, kept a little low as well, went past the outside edge
pitched up outside off, width and Clarke leans into the drive, gets it past mid-off for a couple
low full toss on middle, a couple more as he closes the face and plays this one wide of mid-on
well struck but also well fielded by the bowler, pitched up and it's driven back firmly, the bowler got a hand to it
well timed by Clarke, on a good length, he rocked forward, got across a little and drove it hard past the bowler, past mid-off for a boundary
pitched on a good length, rocks forward and defends it towards cover
flays that one, extra effort needed on this ground since the outfield's slow, in the slot outside off and it's been creamed through extra cover, there is a fielder in the deep but he had no chance
tossed up, bowled full outside off, driven straight to extra cover
shortish on the off, punched off the back foot to extra cover
flighted on the off, that's been pushed back to the bowler
tidy stuff, short of a length, cut but straight to point
floating it outside off, gets forward and stabs that to extra cover
tossed up, drives that one down to long-off for a single, good start by Sadiq
tossed up outside off, pushes that one into the off side
turns in from outside off, gets across and drives it to midwicket
comes down the track and pushes it to long-on for a single
flighted on the off, drives that straight to extra cover
full toss, crunches that down the pitch and into the stumps at the non-striker's end, Ahmadi didn't get a hand to that one
low full toss, pushed it through quicker on the off stump, pushes that towards long-off for a single
pitched on a length, that's been driven towards long-off for a single
full toss outside off, steers that towards third man for a single
short of a length outside off, punched through point for a single
shortish outside off, cut towards third man for a single again
angling in towards middle, gets across to drive it wide of mid-on for a single
angling in towards middle and leg, clipped away through to deep square leg for a single
reaches forward and plays that back to the bowler
comes down the track and defends it to the bowler
drives that one towards long-off for a single
gets on the back foot and tries to tap it into the leg side
chopped past point for a single
shortish on the off, gets on the back foot and he punches it to extra cover
yorker length outside off, failed to dig that one out, went through to the keeper, got a bit of an edge onto the keeper's pad
floating it on the off stump, rocks forward and plays it back to the bowler
flighted on the off, lands full and it's driven through to long-off for a single
shortish on the off, gets on the back foot and chops it to point
flat on middle, gets on the back foot and defends it into the off side
struck hard, on middle and off and it's swept towards deep square leg for a single
shortish on middle, tickled towards square leg for a single
fires it flat on middle, gets on the back foot and taps it wide of midwicket
floating it on the off, gets forward and pushes it to extra cover
shortish outside off, cut away towards point off the back foot
kept low, short outside off, tried to slam it through cover, missed, quicker delivery from Sadiq
Huge appeal for lbw from Shenwari, he was miles down the track and it was missing off
floating it on middle, drives it down the pitch to the bowler
short of a length outside off, chops that one down to point
flatter, comes down the track and pushes it in front of the bowler
gave that a bit of a rip, gets a stride out and defends it into the leg side
shortish outside off, turns away just a hint and he lets it go
shortish on middle, gets on the back foot and punched it towards long-on for a single
shortish outside off, crunched past point for a single
drives that one down the ground for a single
pushed away into the off side
drives that one down the ground towards long-off for a single
dropped, short on the off, drags it hard towards midwicket, a powerful pull and it's been put down at midwicket by Nowroz Mangal, timed his jump well but spilt it
knocks that one into the leg side off the back foot
punched off the back foot past the bowler for a single
flighted on the off, drives it down towards long-off for a single
shortish on middle, pulled away to deep square leg for a single
floated it on leg stump, gets forward and pushes it into the leg side
shortish on leg stump, pushes it through square leg for a single into the deep
round the wicket, angling in towards middle, comes down the track and knocks it into the off side
gets forward, closes the face and tickles it behind square for a single
flighted on middle, comes down the track and drives it to midwicket
short of a good length, punched off the back foot towards extra cover
shortish on leg stump, turns it away through square leg for a single
shortish on middle, goes for the pull, tries to smash it through square leg, struck high on the thigh
reaches forward to that good length ball and defends in front of the bowler
flighted on the off, comes down the track and drives it back to the bowler, well fielded by the bowler off his own bowling
full toss, juicy, on the off, drags it over square leg, struck hard for a one-bounce four
short of a length outside off, chops that one down to point
short and down the leg side, helps that on its way wide of the diving short fine for three runs
offspinner, short of a good length, gets on the back foot and pushes to point
good length on the off, stretches forward and defends to cover
flat outside off, comes down the track and drops it into the leg side
flattish on the off, gets forward and knocks it down into the off side
flighted on middle, turns it away wide of midwicket for a single
pushed it full on middle, gets forward and taps it towards cover
shortish on the off, gets on the back foot and works it past midwicket
flighted on middle, drives it back towards the bowler, he dives and palms it to midwicket
cracked it through extra cover into the deep for a couple of runs
down the leg side, first wide of the innings, raises the 100 for Australia
full toss on the off, drills that down towards long-off for a single
flattish on the off, comes down the track and drives it to long-on for a single
short outside off, cut uppishly into the deep towards point for a single
flighted on leg and middle, gets forward and pushes it towards cover
comes down the track and drives it straight to extra cover again
slides that down the leg side, sweeps it fine for a couple of runs
tossed up on the off, comes down the track and drives it towards extra cover
shapes up for a sweep, comes round the wicket does the bowler, it turns away after pitching and he fails to make contact
tossed up outside off, drives it down to long-off for a single
full toss on middle, drives that towards midwicket from the crease
full toss on middle, driven down to long-on for a single
into the stands, full toss and Clarke doesn't spare it, comes down the track and swings it over the deep square leg boundary
well fielded at midwicket, long hop, moved back and smashed it hard but Nabi fielded it well inside the circle
floating it outside off, turns away and he leaves that one alone to the keeper
full toss, comes down the track and drives it to long-off for a single
flat on the off, comes down the track and pushes it through midwicket for a single
shortish on middle and off, pushes it towards point from the crease
comes down the track as he slowed it down a little, pushes it to cover
fires it full on the off, drives it to long-off for a single
gets to the pitch after coming down the track and drives it to long-on for a single
swept hard towards deep midwicket for a single
flighted, turns out to be a low full toss, drilled down the ground to long-off
tossed up on the off, comes down the track and drives it to long-off
gets front and across and taps it into the leg side in front of square leg
short outside off, waits for it to turn in and slaps it hard to long-on for a single
floating it on middle, gets front and across and defends it back to the bowler
flighted on the off, comes down the track and pushes it back to Shenwari
bowled it with some air on middle, swept towards deep square leg for a single
oversteps, short outside off, chopped towards point, freehit time
full outside off, driven towards deep cover for a single
shortish on leg stump, turned away behind square for a single
comes down the pitch but Shenwari holds it back, plays it back to the bowler
gets across and turns it wide of midwicket for a single to raise his half-century, brings up his 53rd ODI fifty
Wade's turn to reach a ha;f-century, pushes that down to long-off for a single, fifty No.4 for Wade
shortish on middle, punched back down the pitch to the bowler
shortish outside off, crunched towards deep point for a single
flattish outside off, comes down the track and pushes it to midwicket
floating it outside off, driven down towards long-off for a single
flatter on middle, drives that past the bowler to long-off for a single
shortish on the off, turns in and he stabs it in front of cover
short outside leg stump, swept wide of deep square leg for a couple of runs
tossed up on middle, drives it back towards the bowler
comes down the track, he slows it down, pushed back gently to the bowler
shortish outside off, slaps that towards extra cover, there's a misfield there and they run a single
shortish outside off, cracks it past point into the deep for a single
fired flat outside off, cracked through to long-off for a single
looping it towards the off stump, pushes it towards extra cover
shortish outside off, "yeah two, mate" says Wade right after he plays that shot, cuts it past point for a couple

floating it on the off, plays it down towards long-on for a single
comes down the track, gets to the pitch and drives it to long-off for a single
shortish on the off, turns in, gets on the back foot and turned past square leg for a single
flat on middle, comes down the track and turns it through square leg for a single
shortish on the off, pushed from the crease towards extra cover
quicker ball bowled full on middle, pushes it down to long-off for a single
Clarke collects his second six, came down the pitch, took it off a length and smashed it over the deep extra cover boundary, inside out
shortish on the off, turning in, tickles it through square leg for a single
a touch too close to cut there, slowed it up, turned away, he chopped it to point
goodish length on middle, turned past midwicket for a single
the field is in and he finds the gap, short of a length and it's bee cut past point for three runs, he gets one more as the keeper aims at the non-striker's end and misses to concede overthrows
misfield at extra cover, pitched up and that's crunched, mid-off has to give chase, two more
slower one bowled short outside off, happy to get off strike, steered that towards third man for a single, this is highest score in ODIs
some reverse there for Zadran, pitched up on middle and he's smashed it down the ground, Zadran kicks it away and he's in a bit of pain
shortish outside off, cut towards third man for a single
comes down the track and turns it towards short fine
shortish on middle, turns that one wide of short fine for a single
slog-sweep and that's cleared the ropes, fetched it from middle and off, got it in the middle and dispatched it over deep midwicket
followed that up with a quicker delivery, dug out towards square leg for a single
Clarke steps out of the crease and plays it down to long-on for a single
Wade goes, a soft dismissal in the end, bowled it quicker and it was struck well but straight back to the bowler, Nabi reacted well to bend low and take it clean
short of a good length outside off, gets off the mark immediately, guiding that to third man
slower one on middle, turned through square leg for a single
drops that one short outside off, seemed a touch too high, was not called a wide though, he let that one go
short of a good length on the off, gets forward and plays it back to the bowler
slower one bowled short, jabs it through square leg for a single
kept low as he went for the cut, got an inside edge onto his pads
Maxwell has holed out, struck it very well but didn't get the elevation he wanted, struck it flat, tempted by the flight and played it straight down long-on's throat
Clarke gets out of the crease and works that to midwicket
gets on the back foot and tickles it wide of square leg for a single
on leg stump, that's played down in front of square leg for a single
tossed up on middle, drives it down to long-on for a single
tossed up, full toss again, punched through midwicket for a couple of runs
comes down the pitch and pushes that down to long-on for a single
tossed up on the off, rocks forward and defends it to point
shortish on middle and leg, turns it past square leg for a single
tossed up on middle, comes down the track and drives that wide of long-on for a couple of runs

stumped, Clarke just kept walking, was done in by the spin, it turned away as he charged down the pitch to launch him over midwicket, missed, the keeper collected, he was in no hurry to take down the stumps as Clarke had given up and began walking, four down now
angling in towards middle, defended in front of point for a quick single
shortish on the off, gets on the back foot and whips it through midwicket
gets on the back foot and turns it through square leg
turns in from outside off, defended towards extra cover
tossed up on middle, drives it to midwicket, no single conceded there
short on middle, pulled away towards deep square leg for a single
shortish on the off, turns away, gets on the back foot and pushes it to cover
short outside off, cracks it through to deep cover for a single
appeal for lbw, turns in from middle and would have probably missed leg, Hussey may have got an inside edge
pulled that one towards deep square leg for a single
well fielded, tossed up and it was struck back hard at the bowler, he collected it cleanly
waits for it to turn away, cuts it wide of point, no single on offer there
on the pads, turned through midwicket for a single, misfield by the captain there
flat on the off, pushes that down to long-on for a single
Michael Hussey reverse-paddles that to point, sends his brother back as he calls for a single
full on middle, drives it in front of midwicket, Mangal can't prevent the single
shortish on the off, punched to long-off for one more
leading edge as it turns towards off and he tries to close the face, lands in front of point
ooh, that didn't miss the off stump by much, slower through the air and David Hussey was into the pull too early, missed
tossed up on middle, drives it to long-on for a single
short and it's pulled hard, found that gap between deep square leg and deep midwicket
drops that down in front of point for an easy single
short outside off and slow, cut hard through point into the deep for a couple of runs
chipped that one towards long-off on the bounce for a single
flat on middle, turned wide of midwicket for a quick single
shortish on leg stump, turns it wide of square leg for a single
fires it full outside off, drilled towards deep cover for a single
gets forward and knocks it to the left of the bowler for a quick single
shortish on the off, punched wide of point for a single
full toss on middle, driven towards deep midwicket for a single

appeal for caught-behind, there was a sound, pitched on a length outside off, Mike Hussey chases it, did the bat hit the ground? Or was it an edge? Hard to make out from that first replay, bat may have hit the ground there
pinches a single into the off side
goodish length, drives that one straight to extra cover
pitched on a length on the off, drives it towards mid-off for a quick single
slower one bowled short outside off, late-cuts it delicately towards third man for a couple of runs

run-out, yorker length on the off, dug out towards extra cover, excellent fielding there, collects it on the bounce and throws down the stumps at the non-striker's end, David Hussey was sent back, dived and failed to make it back
Misfield by Ahmadi at mid-off, concedes a run as he runs in to stop that
lands full outside off, is steered down to third man for a single
yorker length on the off stump, plays that one back to the bowler
full toss on middle, struck straight to midwicket, no run on offer there
pitched on a length, pushed towards long-off for a single
low full toss on middle, drives that one straight to long-on for a single
fires that a little wide of the off stump, Hussey reaches for that one but misses
short on the off and he dispatches it this time, rocks back and pulls it over midwicket for a boundary
low full toss on middle, digs it into the ground and gets it over the bowler on the bounce for a single
straying on the pads, full toss, clipped past short fine for a couple more runs, Shapoor gives chase
slower one on middle, whipped past square leg for a single
full outside leg stump, almost yorker length, tries to clip it square, gets a leg-bye instead
poor ball from Zadran, was trying the yorker, ends up being the full toss, Hussey scoops that so well that it goes all the way, over short fine and the fine-leg boundary
length ball and that's gone for six as well, in the slot for Hussey on the off stump and it's launched high and handsome over the deep midwicket fence
full on middle, clipped through square leg into the deep for a couple of runs
full toss on leg stump, tried to whack it through short fine, it was there to hit but missed out, got an inside edge onto the pads
yorker length on the off, digs it out in front of extra cover for a single, a quick run as Mangal takes aim at the non-striker's end
full toss outside off, pushed towards long-off for a single
nippy, bowled quick on leg stump, tried to force it through square leg, they get a single
nicely fielded at point, was pitched up outside off, made room and steered it towards that fielder, just a single in the end
slower one bowled on leg, tried to hoick it over short fine, got just the single, another leg bye
down the leg side again and Hussey misses out, fails to help it past short fine, one more leg bye
slower one bowled short, pulls it well, connects it off the middle, pulled away into that gap between deep square leg and deep midwicket
aims for a yorker, driven straight to midwicket, a dot ball, ends his spell
makes a bit of room, he chases him outside leg stump, driven past midwicket for a single to raise the 250
length ball, gives way and clips that delivery over the short fine leg fielder for a boundary

that's disappeared, Bailey has picked that up from a length again, made a bit of room, in landed in the zone on middle and he launched it over the long-on boundary, into the stands, 50-partnership up, off just 27 balls
better from Shapoor, almost gets the yorker right, drives it past midwicket for a single
called a no-ball for height, Hussey came down the track though but it would still comfortably have been above the waist is what the umpires reckon, mistimes a pull towards long-on
pitched up outside off, that's driven straight to extra cover
gets the yorker right but after being hit around, in the blockhole on middle, Bailey fails to dig it out and the stumps take a beating
full toss on the off and Hussey deals with it, thrashes it over long-on for another six, cleanly struck
bowled'im, misses his half-century, shortish on the off, moves away to chop that through point, gets an inside edge onto the stumps
shortish and it kept low, was lucky to get some bat on that as he tried to pull, just the single
flighted outside off, cracked straight to extra cover for a single
Another wicket for Sadiq, slogs at that one, it's a straight ball from round the wicket, misses it completely and is bowled
fullish outside off, dug out past cover, collects a single

inn2.comm: excellent start, a full delivery on the pads and that's been driven hard through midwicket for a boundary, firmly hit
shaping away there, in the channel outside off and he leaves that one alone to the keeper
short of a good length, gets on the back foot and drops it into the leg side in front of the bowler
drops that short on the leg stump, turns that away towards fine leg for a single
pitched on a length on the off, that's been pushed straight to mid-off
short of a length outside off, tries to cut that past point, doesn't make contact
the ball curves in there, swung in to land on a good length outside off, mistimes an attempted drive to mid-off
pitched up on middle, bowled quick and got it to swing in, just managed to get some bat on it, an inside edge onto the pads
short of a good length on the off, rocks back and pushes it to extra cover
goodish length outside off, tries to crash it through extra cover, misses and so does Wade, who concedes a bye, good carry there
bowled'im! Quick and it swung in to castle him, landed on middle, was late in bringing his bat down to play it, got an inside edge and was bowled, an early loss for Afghanistan
in the channel outside off stump and he lets that one go through
short of a good length, punched wide of mid-off for a single
this one came back in, got forward and got a thick inside edge towards square leg
they like playing their shots, dropped it short on the off, pulled but straight to midwicket, kept it down
bowled that one in the channel outside off, moving away and it's left alone
a touch too wide there and it's called by the umpire, he leaves that one alone
edged and goes down towards third man, didn't go hard at that one, all along the ground for a single
Sadiq drives that one sweetly, pitched on a length outside off, straight to mid-off
short of a good length outside off and it's been left alone to the keeper
shortish on the off, played it towards square leg for a single
shortish on the off, gets on the back foot and crunches it to point
slashed hard, short of a good length, tried to smack it over point, got a thick outside edge well past second slip for a boundary
dropped it short on middle, ducks under that one and lets it be
goes over point, on a good length and he slices that over the in-field, got a good amount of bat on it, earns a boundary
boundaries flowing for Afghanistan, short and wide and he gets into position early to smack it through point
beaten, bowled from slightly wide of the crease, short of a good length and moved away, pushed at it and missed
in the channel outside off stump, a bit of away movement there, left alone to the keeper
shortish on the off, pushed from the crease towards cover
fires it full on middle, plays it out towards mid-on from the crease, attempted yorker
short of a good length on the off, rocked back to defend, got an inside edge and dropped into the leg side

struck on the helmet, dropped it short and it nipped back in, was too late to react there, tried to duck but in vain, got him hard on the helmet, Starc immediately asks him if he's doing fine and he is
he's lost his bat, heaved that one, didn't connect as well as he would have liked though, past square leg for a couple of runs
fierce bowling from Starc, tries to fend that one away, short ball, sharp and it nips back in, comes off the glove and then the helmet, goes towards fine leg
ooh, lovely delivery, curving in again and he just managed to get his bat down in time, almost yorker length, gets an inside edge for a single
Through the gate, Sadiq has been given a tough time, short of a good length, got it to nip back in and Sadiq, played a little outside the line to that one, was bowled between bat and pad
short of a good length on the off, rocks back and taps it towards point
starts off with a widish delivery, slightly short and it keeps low, left alone to the keeper
well fielded at cover point, short of a good length and it's crunched hard into the ground, Maxwell throws himself to his left
short of a good length, runs that towards third man for a single
wide, too wide, full and Shehzad doesn't need to play at that one
pulled hard, took his eyes off the ball for a moment there, dropped that short did Johnson and it was played to fine leg
shortish on middle, turned towards fine leg for a single
goodish length on the off, rocks on the back foot and defends it towards cover
down the leg side, some swing there but misdirected, a single to the score courtesy a wide
swinging in, on middle, flicked away through square leg into the deep for a couple of runs
shortish outside off, chopped into the ground towards point
low full toss outside off, he didn't see that coming did Stanikzai, defended awkwardly towards point
in the channel outside off, leaves that one alone to the keeper
short and he sensed a chance, shaped up for a pull but it came on to him a little quickly, got an inside edge onto the ribs
slides down the leg side, full and down the leg side, clipped past short fine to the boundary, did it come off the pads? Starc appealed for lbw but that was missing leg anyway
a full toss well outside off, tries to flay that through the covers, gets an inside edge towards the keeper
short of a good length, punched wide of extra cover for a single
beaten, on a length outside off, gets forward to defend but is late on the shot, goes past the outside edge
shortish on the off, rocks back and taps that towards point from the crease
pitched up and he drives that well but straight to cover point, hit hard into the ground
beaten, this one moved away just a hint and Stanikzai got forward to that good length ball, just went past the outside edge
